cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the application of reinforcement learning algorithms on a robot, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of slow feature analysis (SFA) for filtering sensor readings is a machine learning technique, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The sensor used is a head-mounted video camera, which involves computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the representation of environmental states, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
